导消费者」等行为立案调查，其将承担哪些法律责任？消费者可如何维权？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "9 月 17 日，合肥高新区市场监督管理局发布情况通报：近日，三只羊网络科技有限公司直播带货的「香港美诚月饼」引发关注。对三只羊网络科技有限公司在直播中涉嫌「误导消费者」等行为，现已立案调查，将根据调查结果依法依规处理。我局联合相关部门已多次约谈督促企业规范经营行为，对企业直播带货中出现的违法违规行为将坚决依法查处。 合肥高新区市场监督管理局：对三只羊在直播中涉嫌「误导消费者」等行为立案调查 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-62643f7b130e32b516ab1f150a426f71_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667389119"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz9HQ3/TY+phUEAMaCTExMDU4NjUyOSCVgKS3BjAAONUDQAVyCTY2NzM4OTExOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1726575507.313615", "card_id": "Q_666786197", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价肖央、宋佳主演的电影《祝你幸福！》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-737dd22e0b701836214b482f779a4bc5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666786197"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iz9HQ3/TY+phUEAMaCTExMDQ1MjUzMiDWsYG3BjAAOBpABnIJNjY2Nzg2MTk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1726575507.313938", "card_id": "Q_664544875", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"t